productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Sao Tome and Principe and I bought one.
My co-worker Skylar has one of these. He says it looks sweaty.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Generic Rubber Chair keeps them away.
one of my hobbies is mushroom cultivation. and when i'm cultivating mushrooms this works great.
